    "bodyJa": "## ac-web-static2 をリリースする\n\n1. **以下の PR をマージする**\n\n   - [ ] ac-web-static2  \n          https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/pull/XXX  \n          ※ PR リンクは必ず変更する\n\n2. **main ブランチの CI が成功していることを確認する**\n\n   - [ ] [GitHub Actions](https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/actions/workflows/ci.yml) で CI ビルドが成功していることを確認する\n\n3. **ステージングにデプロイする**\n\n   - [ ] `npm run deploy:stg` を実行する\n   - [ ] https://stg.air-closet.com で変更内容を確認する\n\n4. **本番にデプロイする**\n\n   - [ ] `npm run deploy:prod` を実行する\n\n5. **リリース完了の確認**\n   - [ ] https://www.air-closet.com で変更内容が正しく反映されていることを確認する",
    "bodyEn": "## Release ac-web-static2\n\n1. **Merge the following PR**\n\n   - [ ] ac-web-static2  \n          https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/pull/XXX  \n          Update the PR link as needed\n\n2. **Wait for CI to pass on main**\n\n   - [ ] Confirm CI build succeeded in [GitHub Actions](https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n\n3. **Deploy to staging**\n\n   - [ ] Execute `npm run deploy:stg`\n   - [ ] Verify changes on https://stg.air-closet.com\n\n4. **Deploy to production**\n\n   - [ ] Execute `npm run deploy:prod`\n\n5. **Verify the release**\n   - [ ] Verify that the changes are correctly reflected on https://www.air-closet.com",
    "bodyVi": "## Release ac-web-static2\n\n1. **Merge PR sau**\n\n   - [ ] ac-web-static2  \n          https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/pull/XXX  \n          ※ Nhớ thay đổi link PR\n\n2. **Xác nhận CI trên branch main đã thành công**\n\n   - [ ] Xác nhận CI build đã thành công trên [GitHub Actions](https://github.com/air-closet/ac-web-static2/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n\n3. **Deploy lên staging**\n\n   - [ ] Chạy `npm run deploy:stg`\n   - [ ] Xác nhận các thay đổi trên https://stg.air-closet.com\n\n4. **Deploy lên production**\n\n   - [ ] Chạy `npm run deploy:prod`\n\n5. **Xác nhận release hoàn tất**\n   - [ ] Xác nhận các thay đổi đã được phản ánh đúng trên https://www.air-closet.com"
