    "bodyEn": "## Release air-closet-styling-console\n\n1. **Merge the following PR**\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-styling-console\n          https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-styling-console/pull/593  \n          Update the PR link as needed\n\n2. **Release air-closet-console to pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] Release `ac-console-app-prod` following the procedure below  \n          https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n\n3. **Release air-closet-styling-console to pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] Execute `npm run deploy:pre-prod`\n   - [ ] Confirm the branch name is master\n   - [ ] Confirm the deployed commit SHA1 is the latest master SHA1\n   - [ ] After deployment, access the URL below and confirm the SHA1 matches  \n          https://console-black.air-closet.com/styling-console/release-version\n\n4. **Verify functionality in pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] User detail page is displayed\n   - [ ] Styling submission can be sent  \n          (Use a test user and revert to pre-selection state afterward)\n\n5. **Release air-closet-styling-console to production**\n\n   - [ ] Execute `npm run deploy:prod`\n   - [ ] Confirm the branch name is master\n   - [ ] Confirm the deployed commit SHA1 is the latest master SHA1\n   - [ ] Verify the SHA1 at the following URL  \n          https://console.air-closet.com/styling-console/release-version\n\n6. **Verify functionality in production**\n   - [ ] User detail page is displayed\n   - [ ] Styling submission can be sent  \n          (Use a test user and revert to pre-selection state afterward)",
