    "bodyJa": "## air-closet-styling-api のリリース\n\n1. **以下の PR をマージする**\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-styling-api\n         https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-styling-api/pull/xxxx\n         ※ PR リンクは必ず変更する\n\n2. **air-closet-infrastructure にリリース対象の SHA1 をセットする**\n\n   - [ ] `air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars/ac-styling-console-api-prod.yml` の\n         `release_sha1` を最新の `master` の SHA1 に更新する\n   - [ ] 以下を実行する\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX`（変更必須）\n         `git commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"`\n         `git push origin master`\n\n3. **プレ本番環境にリリースする**\n\n   - [ ] 以下の手順に従って `ac-styling-console-api-prod` をリリースする\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] デプロイ後、以下 URL にアクセスし\n         `X-Ac-Api-Revision` が `master` の SHA1 と一致していることを確認する\n         https://styling-api-black.air-closet.com/status\n\n4. **プレ本番環境で動作確認を行う**\n\n   - [ ] ユーザーカルテが表示される\n   - [ ] 選定送信ができる\n         （テストユーザーで実行し、送信後は「選定前に戻す」こと）\n\n5. **本番環境にリリースする**\n\n   - [ ] 以下の手順に従って `ac-styling-console-api-prod` をリリースする\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] `X-Ac-Api-Revision` が `master` の SHA1 と一致することを確認する\n         https://styling-api.air-closet.com/status\n\n6. **本番環境で動作確認を行う**\n   - [ ] ユーザーカルテが表示される\n   - [ ] 選定送信ができる",
    "bodyEn": "## Release air-closet-styling-api\n\n1. **Merge the following PR**\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-styling-api\n         https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-styling-api/pull/xxxx\n         Update the PR link as needed\n\n2. **Set the release SHA1 in air-closet-infrastructure**\n\n   - [ ] Update `release_sha1` in\n         `air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars/ac-styling-console-api-prod.yml`\n         to the latest SHA1 of the `master` branch\n   - [ ] Execute the following\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX` (Required)\n         `git commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"`\n         `git push origin master`\n\n3. **Release to pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] Release `ac-styling-console-api-prod` following the procedure below\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] After deployment, confirm `X-Ac-Api-Revision` matches the `master` SHA1\n         https://styling-api-black.air-closet.com/status\n\n4. **Verify functionality in pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] User chart is displayed\n   - [ ] Styling submission works\n         (Use a test user and revert after submission)\n\n5. **Release to production**\n\n   - [ ] Release `ac-styling-console-api-prod` following the procedure below\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] Confirm `X-Ac-Api-Revision` matches the `master` SHA1\n         https://styling-api.air-closet.com/status\n\n6. **Verify functionality in production**\n   - [ ] User chart is displayed\n   - [ ] Styling submission works",
    "bodyVi": "## Release air-closet-styling-api\n\n1. **Merge PR bên dưới**\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-styling-api\n         https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-styling-api/pull/xxxx\n         Cần thay đổi link PR cho đúng\n\n2. **Cập nhật SHA1 release trong air-closet-infrastructure**\n\n   - [ ] Cập nhật `release_sha1` trong\n         `air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars/ac-styling-console-api-prod.yml`\n         thành SHA1 mới nhất của nhánh `master`\n   - [ ] Thực hiện các lệnh sau\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX` (Bắt buộc)\n         `git commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"`\n         `git push origin master`\n\n3. **Release lên môi trường pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] Release `ac-styling-console-api-prod` theo hướng dẫn sau\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] Sau khi deploy, kiểm tra `X-Ac-Api-Revision` trùng với SHA1 của `master`\n         https://styling-api-black.air-closet.com/status\n\n4. **Kiểm tra chức năng trên môi trường pre-production**\n\n   - [ ] Hiển thị user chart\n   - [ ] Gửi chọn đồ thành công\n         (Dùng user test và hoàn tác sau khi gửi)\n\n5. **Release lên môi trường production**\n\n   - [ ] Release `ac-styling-console-api-prod` theo hướng dẫn sau\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594\n   - [ ] Kiểm tra `X-Ac-Api-Revision` trùng với SHA1 của `master`\n         https://styling-api.air-closet.com/status\n\n6. **Kiểm tra chức năng trên môi trường production**\n   - [ ] Hiển thị user chart\n   - [ ] Gửi chọn đồ thành công"
