    "bodyJa": "## air-closet-next-warehouse のリリース\n\n1. 以下の PR の「Merge pull request」を押下する\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-next-warehouse: https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-next-warehouse/pull/820\n\n1. air-closet-infrastructure にリリース対象の SHA1 をセットする\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars 配下の対象ファイルの release_sha1 を最新の master の SHA1 に更新\n   - [ ] 以下を実行\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX <- 変更必須 / Điền mã project\ngit commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"\ngit push origin master`\n\n1. プレ本番環境にリリースする\n\n   - [ ] リンク先の手順に従い `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod` をリリース\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n\n1. プレ本番環境でテストする\n\n   - [ ] ログインできる\n   - [ ] 過去アイテムが表示され、購入ボタンが表示される\n   - URL: https://prod-black.air-closet.com/\n\n1. 本番環境にリリースする\n\n   - [ ] リンク先の手順に従い `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod` をリリース\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n   - [ ] 完了後ターミナルで下記を実行し、`X-Ac-Api-Revision` が master SHA1 と一致することを確認\n         `curl -s --dump-header - https://next-warehouse.air-closet.com/status | grep -i 'x-ac-api-revision' | awk '{print \"released SHA1: \" $2}' | tr -d '\\r'`\n\n1. 本番環境でテストする\n   - [ ] ログインできる\n   - [ ] 過去アイテムが表示され、購入ボタンが表示される",
    "bodyEn": "## Release air-closet-next-warehouse\n\n1. Click \"Merge pull request\" on the following PR\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-next-warehouse: https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-next-warehouse/pull/820\n\n1. Set release SHA1 in air-closet-infrastructure\n\n   - [ ] Update release_sha1 in the target file under air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars to the latest master SHA1\n   - [ ] Execute the following\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX <- update project code\ngit commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"\ngit push origin master`\n\n1. Release to pre-production\n\n   - [ ] Follow the guide to release `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod`\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n\n1. Test in pre-production\n\n   - [ ] Can log in\n   - [ ] Past items display and purchase button shows\n   - URL: https://prod-black.air-closet.com/\n\n1. Release to production\n\n   - [ ] Follow the guide to release `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod`\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n   - [ ] After completion, run the following in terminal to confirm `X-Ac-Api-Revision` matches master SHA1\n         curl -s --dump-header - https://next-warehouse.air-closet.com/status | grep -i 'x-ac-api-revision' | awk '{print \"released SHA1: \" $2}' | tr -d '\\r'\n\n1. Test in production\n   - [ ] Can log in\n   - [ ] Past items display and purchase button shows",
    "bodyVi": "## Release air-closet-next-warehouse\n\n1. Nhấn \"Merge pull request\" trên PR sau\n\n   - [ ] air-closet-next-warehouse: https://github.com/air-closet/air-closet-next-warehouse/pull/820\n\n1. Cập nhật SHA1 release trong air-closet-infrastructure\n\n   - [ ] Cập nhật release_sha1 trong file target dưới air-closet-infrastructure/ansible/group_vars với SHA1 mới nhất của master\n   - [ ] Thực hiện các lệnh sau\n         `PROJECT_NO=AIRCLOSET-XXXXX <- cập nhật mã dự án\ngit commit -am \":rocket:$PROJECT_NO: release to prod\"\ngit push origin master`\n\n1. Release lên pre-production\n\n   - [ ] Thực hiện theo hướng dẫn để release `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod`\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n\n1. Kiểm tra trên pre-production\n\n   - [ ] Đăng nhập được\n   - [ ] Hiển thị các món trước đó và nút mua hiển thị\n   - URL: https://prod-black.air-closet.com/\n\n1. Release lên production\n\n   - [ ] Thực hiện theo hướng dẫn để release `ac-next-warehouse-api-prod`\n         https://air-closet.esa.io/posts/1594#ansible%E3%82%92%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AC%E3%83%9D%E3%82%B8%E3%83%88%E3%83%AA%E3%82%92%E6%9C%AC%E7%95%AA%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E3%81%AB%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99)\n   - [ ] Sau khi hoàn tất, chạy lệnh sau để xác nhận `X-Ac-Api-Revision` trùng với SHA1 của master\n         curl -s --dump-header - https://next-warehouse.air-closet.com/status | grep -i 'x-ac-api-revision' | awk '{print \"released SHA1: \" $2}' | tr -d '\\r'\n\n1. Kiểm tra trên production\n   - [ ] Đăng nhập được\n   - [ ] Hiển thị các món trước đó và nút mua hiển thị"
