    "bodyEn": "**1. Merge Pull Request**\n\n- [ ] **bridge-api**: https://github.com/air-closet/bridge-api/pull/xxx\n\n**2. Build & Deploy via AWS CLI**\n\n```bash\n# List available services through SSM\nssm-start-session\n\n# Select the 'bridge-deploy' service\nbridge-deploy\n\n# Switch to the ec2-user account\nsudo su - ec2-user\n\n# Move to the ecspresso directory\ncd bridge-api/ecspresso\n\n# Run the deploy script for the production environment\nsh deploy.sh prod\n```",
