    "name": "Release acm-infra",
    "repo": "acm-infra",
    "bodyJa": "1. **以下の PR をマージする**\n\n   - [ ] acm-infra\n         https://github.com/air-closet/acm-infra/pull/??\n         ※ PR 番号を入力\n\n2. **本番にリリースする**\n\n   - [ ] 以下のコマンドを実行する\n         ```bash\n         git checkout master\n         git pull origin master\n         cd payment-batch/ecrobo-batch\n         make release-prod\n         ```\n\n3. **新しいバージョンを ECR にアップロードする**\n\n   - [ ] README.md に従って実行\n\n4. **リビジョンを変更する**\n\n   - [ ] タスクフォルダに移動する\n         ```bash\n         cd <acm-api/ecrobo-batch/payment-batch>/deploy/prod\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] リビジョン変更コマンドを実行する\n         ```bash\n         ./update-task.sh\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] 更新するタスクとバージョンを選択\n         例: `ecrobo_order: arn:aws:ecs:ap-northeast-1:784286759117:task-definition/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod:195`\n\n   - [ ] タスク、現在のリビジョン、更新リビジョンを確認\n\n5. **リリースできているかの確認**\n\n   - [ ] スクリプトは正常に実行され、新しいリビジョンが表示される\n   - [ ] 可能であれば、AWS コンソールの画面を確認する\n\n#### 新しいバッチを追加する場合\n\n- [ ] AWS に新しいバッチを追加\n  1. https://ap-northeast-1.console.aws.amazon.com/ecs/v2/clusters/acm-infra-prod-20191107/scheduled-tasks/create にアクセス\n  2. 以下の内容を入力:\n     ```\n     Schedule rule name:\n     Scheduled rule description:\n     Schedule rule: turned on\n     Cron expression: cron(0 17 * * ? *)\n     Target ID:\n     Task definition family: acm-infra-payment-batch-prod/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod\n     Task definition revision: latest\n     VPC: acm-prod-vpc\n     subnet: acm-prod-public-1a, acm-prod-public-1c\n     Security group: Use an existing security group\n     Security group name: acm-infra-prod-sg\n     Public IP: turned on\n     Container overrides の Command override で command をコピー\n     （<./payment,process_user_blacklist or ./ecrobo,stop_rental>）\n     Environment variable overrides: key (ENV) value (production)\n     ```",
    "bodyEn": "1. **Merge the following PR**\n\n   - [ ] acm-infra\n         https://github.com/air-closet/acm-infra/pull/??\n         ※ Enter PR number\n\n2. **Release to production**\n\n   - [ ] Execute the following commands\n         ```bash\n         git checkout master\n         git pull origin master\n         cd payment-batch/ecrobo-batch\n         make release-prod\n         ```\n\n3. **Upload new version to ECR**\n\n   - [ ] Follow README.md instructions\n\n4. **Update revision**\n\n   - [ ] Navigate to task directory\n         ```bash\n         cd <acm-api/ecrobo-batch/payment-batch>/deploy/prod\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] Run update revision command\n         ```bash\n         ./update-task.sh\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] Select task and version to update\n         E.g: `ecrobo_order: arn:aws:ecs:ap-northeast-1:784286759117:task-definition/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod:195`\n\n   - [ ] Confirm task, current revision, and update revision\n\n5. **Confirm release was successful**\n\n   - [ ] Script executed successfully and new revision is displayed\n   - [ ] If possible, check revision on AWS console screen\n\n#### Adding a new batch\n\n- [ ] Add new batch to AWS\n  1. Go to https://ap-northeast-1.console.aws.amazon.com/ecs/v2/clusters/acm-infra-prod-20191107/scheduled-tasks/create\n  2. Fill in with details:\n     ```\n     Schedule rule name:\n     Scheduled rule description:\n     Schedule rule: turned on\n     Cron expression: cron(0 17 * * ? *)\n     Target ID:\n     Task definition family: acm-infra-payment-batch-prod/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod\n     Task definition revision: latest\n     VPC: acm-prod-vpc\n     subnet: acm-prod-public-1a, acm-prod-public-1c\n     Security group: Use an existing security group\n     Security group name: acm-infra-prod-sg\n     Public IP: turned on\n     Container overrides Command override: copy command\n     (<./payment,process_user_blacklist or ./ecrobo,stop_rental>)\n     Environment variable overrides: key (ENV) value (production)\n     ```",
    "bodyVi": "1. **Merge PR sau**\n\n   - [ ] acm-infra\n         https://github.com/air-closet/acm-infra/pull/??\n         ※ Điền số PR\n\n2. **Release lên production**\n\n   - [ ] Chạy các lệnh sau\n         ```bash\n         git checkout master\n         git pull origin master\n         cd payment-batch/ecrobo-batch\n         make release-prod\n         ```\n\n3. **Upload phiên bản mới lên ECR**\n\n   - [ ] Thực hiện theo README.md\n\n4. **Update revision**\n\n   - [ ] Di chuyển đến thư mục task\n         ```bash\n         cd <acm-api/ecrobo-batch/payment-batch>/deploy/prod\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] Chạy lệnh update revision\n         ```bash\n         ./update-task.sh\n         ```\n\n   - [ ] Chọn task và version cần update\n         VD: `ecrobo_order: arn:aws:ecs:ap-northeast-1:784286759117:task-definition/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod:195`\n\n   - [ ] Xác nhận task, revision hiện tại và revision mới\n\n5. **Xác nhận đã release thành công**\n\n   - [ ] Script chạy thành công và hiển thị revision mới\n   - [ ] Nếu có thể, kiểm tra revision trên màn hình AWS console\n\n#### Thêm batch mới\n\n- [ ] Thêm batch mới vào AWS\n  1. Truy cập https://ap-northeast-1.console.aws.amazon.com/ecs/v2/clusters/acm-infra-prod-20191107/scheduled-tasks/create\n  2. Điền các thông tin sau:\n     ```\n     Schedule rule name:\n     Scheduled rule description:\n     Schedule rule: turned on\n     Cron expression: cron(0 17 * * ? *)\n     Target ID:\n     Task definition family: acm-infra-payment-batch-prod/acm-infra-ecrobo-batch-prod\n     Task definition revision: latest\n     VPC: acm-prod-vpc\n     subnet: acm-prod-public-1a, acm-prod-public-1c\n     Security group: Use an existing security group\n     Security group name: acm-infra-prod-sg\n     Public IP: turned on\n     Container overrides Command override: copy command\n     (<./payment,process_user_blacklist or ./ecrobo,stop_rental>)\n     Environment variable overrides: key (ENV) value (production)\n     ```"
